            <title><![CDATA[反腐短片透露落马原市委书记 三年五餐饭收540万元人民币]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>中</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>共<span><span><span><span><span><span><span>湖南省纪律检查委员会湖南省监察委员会</span>推出《忠诚与背叛》· 2022湖南反腐警示录短视频系列，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>片中披露</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>湖南省常德市委原书记杨懿文案。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
